The legal basis of the processing is Art. 6 para. 1 p. 1 lit. f GDPR. We have a legitimate interest in automating processes and communication with our clients.
The data will be deleted when the purpose of its collection has ceased to apply and there is no obligation to retain it. Further information is available in the provider's privacy policy at
https://www.make.com/en/privacy-notice
