We use AdRoll for personalized advertising campaigns and retargeting. The provider is AdRoll, a division of NextRoll, Inc., 2300 Harrison St, Fl 2, San Francisco, CA 94110, USA. The provider processes usage data (e.g., visited websites, interest in products or content, access times) and meta/communication data (e.g., device information, IP addresses).
The legal basis of the processing is Art. 6 para. 1 p. 1 lit. a GDPR. The processing is based on consent. Data subjects can revoke their consent at any time by contacting us, for example, using the contact details provided in our privacy policy. The revocation does not affect the lawfulness of the processing until the revocation.
The collected data will be deleted once the purpose of its collection ceases to apply and there are no legal retention obligations. Further information is available in the provider’s privacy policy at:
https://www.adroll.com/about/privacy
.
