or of a prospect (a company that is in the process of becoming Aircall Customer) who acts as our Customer’s agent. If you are an Aircall User, Sections 1 and 5—12 apply to Aircall’s processing of your Personal Data. Also, Aircall likely processes, acting as a Data Processor, your Personal Data for other purposes than those stated herein. For more information about such processing (as well as for exercising your rights related to Personal Data Processing) you should contact the corresponding Aircall Customer in the first instance.
