To the extent that our activities are regulated by EU laws (typically if you are an EU resident) and if you are Aircall Customer, we have a legitimate interest to contact you within our email marketing campaigns. We have a strong belief that you want to be informed about news related to our product and services, as you already benefit from them.
However, if you are not an Aircall customer, we are typically required by applicable law (such as ePrivacy Directive and derived national laws) to rely on your consent. Thus we only contact you via email if you give us such consent (opt-in).
