Sub-policy 5
https://mapme.com/privacy-policy/:
Mapme Privacy Policy
Effective Date: August 11, 2021
Welcome to Mapme.com’s Privacy Policy!
Mapme cares about the privacy of its visitors and users and is fully committed to protecting their personal information and using it properly in compliance with data privacy laws. This policy describes how we may collect and use personal information, and the rights and choices available to our visitors and users regarding such information.
We strongly urge you to read this policy and make sure you fully understand it, before you access or use any of our services.
This privacy policy covers the use of Mapme Story platform and the Mapme website.
Information collected?
Our goal is to collect as little information as possible i.e. we only collect information that is absolutely necessary to provide our service.
We created a table to provide a simple view of the information we collect, why we collect it, and how.
We have 3 groups of users
Users’ users:
people who view the maps either embedded on a website, on social media, or through a direct URL to the map.
Website visitors:
people who visit our website to learn about the Mapme service
Users:
people who create a Mapme account in order to build an interactive map using the Mapme service
We collect 2 types of information
Personal Information
which could be used to uniquely identify an individual.
Non-personal Information
which is non-identifying.
Our Users’ users
